    "enabled": true,
    "includeHidden": false,
    "metadata": {
      "description": "<IMG> element must have non-empty alt attribute to provide meaningful description.",
      "help": "To fix this issue, meaningful description must be provided to all the informative images via alt attribute. Don't leave the alt attribute empty and ensure to have informative text without any junk. Benificial to all the users who perceive the images/ icons without vision.",
